{"tid":2330343,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"標普全球評級將特斯拉(TSLA.US)評級上調至BB，展望為積極","createTime":"2020-12-18T02:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T04:11:31.000Z","uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f3325bd0e22c67bdb2fbd909f04d01cda2ee797","tid":2330343,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T02:41:57.000Z","msg":"標普全球評級目前將其特斯拉(<a href=\"http://TSLA.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTSLA.US&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=d0f2f2c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">TSLA.US</a>)評級（包括發行人信用評級）從&ldquo;BB-&rdquo;上調至&ldquo;BB&rdquo;,前景展望由穩定調整為積極，距投資級別還有兩步之遙。<br />\n<br />\n標普表示，該公司2020年全年的股權出售增加了其流動性，並大大降低了公司的財務風險。預計到2020年底，特斯拉的現金持有量將超過190億美元。<br />\n<br />\n該機構補充道：&ldquo;特斯拉似乎很容易為其在中國和歐洲等全球市場的擴張提供資金，並通過在得克薩斯州開設工廠來擴大其在美國的製造基地。&rdquo;如果特斯拉的競爭優勢能顯著加強，未來12個月內該機構或有33%的可能性繼續上調該公司的評級。"},{"pid":"9dcd2a930c8f1464f29a65e9585ce63dfcece1fd","tid":2330343,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T02:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6567ba2b0a91d9d2abd4f84dfde729ccd225accc","tid":2330343,"uid":180538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直線上升"},{"pid":"bed1a621a264f1b6305b0322b9b16b9da6c48150","tid":2330343,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6567ba2b0a91d9d2abd4f84dfde729ccd225accc","tid":2330343,"uid":180538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\